snippet.title: PlayStation - Zoku Mikagura Shoujo Tanteidan ~Kanketsuhen~ (1999)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Zoku Mikagura Shoujo Tanteidan ~Kanketsuhen~ is an Adventure game, developed and published by Human Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 1999.
